<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 11:35:27 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>人狗漫步高楼间</title><link>https://some.pics/69db837c3c44d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一个男人和他的狗在高楼大厦间漫步。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A man and his dog strolled between tall buildings." height="4160" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/yvan/69db837c3c44d.jpg" width="6240"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://yvan.some.pics"&gt;@yvan&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 11:35:27 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>赏景</title><link>https://some.pics/69db8006b935c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;欣赏风景&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Enjoying the view" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/andyn/69db8006b935c.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://andyn.some.pics"&gt;@andyn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 11:20:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>历史银行餐厅美食体验</title><link>https://some.pics/69db769ed9fd8</link><description>&lt;p&gt;昨晚我们在蓝岭市中心的The General Ledger吃了晚餐。这是一家开在历史悠久的银行建筑内的餐厅和酒吧。你甚至可以在旧金库里就座。我尝了他们的招牌菜之一，黑猪排配培根苹果酸辣酱和土豆泥。味道很棒，是我此行目前最喜欢的一餐。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='Historic building with a marble facade, labeled "General Ledger," featuring two-story windows, flower boxes, and a welcoming entrance, exuding charm.' height="3572" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69db769ed9fd8.jpg" width="2679"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 10:40:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>历史银行餐厅美食体验</title><link>https://some.pics/69db766e5f40c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;昨晚我们在蓝岭市中心的The General Ledger吃了晚餐。这是一家开在历史悠久的银行建筑内的餐厅和酒吧。你甚至可以在旧金库里就座。我尝了他们的招牌菜之一，黑猪排配培根苹果酸辣酱和土豆泥。味道很棒，是我此行目前最喜欢的一餐。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A savory pork chop topped with apples and bacon, served with mashed potatoes and broccolini on a white plate. The dish looks hearty and appetizing." height="2710" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69db766e5f40c.jpg" width="3614"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 10:39:45 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>蓝岭梅尔西果园</title><link>https://some.pics/69db7641a7091</link><description>&lt;p&gt;位于佐治亚州蓝岭的梅西尔果园是一家备受好评的家族农场，占地300英亩，以其"自摘"苹果体验、烘焙坊和市场而闻名。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Exterior of Mercier Orchards with a colorful sign featuring a large apple. Signs for bakery and winery are visible. Relaxed, inviting atmosphere." height="2962" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69db7641a7091.jpg" width="3949"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 10:39:00 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>